You may use the software for noncommercial purposes only. You may not sell the software. You may not provide the software for use with a fee or other consideration. You may not use the software for advertising, marketing, or to promote any third-party products or services. You may not sublicense the software.

You may make necessary changes to use the software for your own personal or internal business purposes. However, you may not distribute modified versions.

Patents
The licensor grants you a patent license only to make, have made, use, and import the software for noncommercial purposes.

